00:40:21,695 --> 00:40:22,898
What?

587
00:40:25,503 --> 00:40:27,036
Charlie, it was horrible.

588
00:40:27,071 --> 00:40:30,405
He said something about how
he knew I could keep a secret.

589
00:40:30,440 --> 00:40:33,110
What do you mean? What do
you mean he touched you?

590
00:40:35,482 --> 00:40:36,750
You know what I mean.

591
00:40:39,051 --> 00:40:41,101
He groped me and he said something

592
00:40:41,390 --> 00:40:43,034
about he sees what you're doing

593
00:40:43,059 --> 00:40:45,462
and he's waiting for you to slip up and...

594
00:40:59,377 --> 00:41:00,645
Charlie.

595
00:41:06,723 --> 00:41:10,127
- You have to do something.
- (Drawer slams)

596
00:41:13,331 --> 00:41:14,565
Like what?

597
00:41:16,133 --> 00:41:17,268
I don't know.

598
00:41:20,862 --> 00:41:22,562
Men will be men.

599
00:41:24,319 --> 00:41:26,686
Best thing you can do
is stay out of his way.

